{"tid":404494,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"<求救> 流浪狗","createTime":"2017-09-18T06:55:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T14:58:45.000Z","uid":38248,"like":42,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"51d6b32b24211e9121320a22e82d1acb431c0b46","tid":404494,"uid":38248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:55:32.000Z","msg":"其實係吹水台開過，但無乜回應<br />\n<br />\n篇文有d長，希望大家比d耐心睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事源我妹係澳門讀書，佢定期會去路環餵流浪狗，佢地一家六口原本生活得好好<br />\n<br />\n星期三下午再去睇佢地既時候發現得翻四隻，其中有一隻全身癱瘓，當時即刻送左佢去醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/173254_12e840bb319e3aa9dd4213d697fb5444.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F173254_12e840bb319e3aa9dd4213d697fb5444.jpg&h=ebde5a17&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/173255_4cdf6fd1b9b8c49e365ff81533392245.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F173255_4cdf6fd1b9b8c49e365ff81533392245.jpg&h=57dc1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/173257_0b6208f003c2afa05e51e28554b1586a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F173257_0b6208f003c2afa05e51e28554b1586a.jpg&h=f87e1ec1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/173259_eaa691cea3fa09d4e1282332e1b11601.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F173259_eaa691cea3fa09d4e1282332e1b11601.jpg&h=43abbaad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/173300_91695d824db0441124ddba77b42edd77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F173300_91695d824db0441124ddba77b42edd77.jpg&h=0947c5b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n醫生護士第一時間幫老虎仔（我地改既名）降溫，老虎仔既血壓超高同體溫過高(42℃)，有生命危險，醫生話佢嚴重中暑導致四肢暫時癱瘓失去知覺<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/173912_a25b9711eed4ec75421624f7ca8b9854.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F173912_a25b9711eed4ec75421624f7ca8b9854.jpg&h=955b3b16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而家已經第四日，醫生原本話老虎仔三四就可以行得翻，雖然已經脫離左危險期，但都仲係四肢癱瘓，眼見佢愈黎愈冇心機同埋開始唔肯食野<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/174122_91667cf975bdb6e00435491aa2c62f16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F174122_91667cf975bdb6e00435491aa2c62f16.jpg&h=fd3607ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/174123_9685d04161378b2d29c5463c5c27b99f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F174123_9685d04161378b2d29c5463c5c27b99f.jpg&h=ff83ad53&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/174124_90157304ee8f6228eb60cd560ad517f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F174124_90157304ee8f6228eb60cd560ad517f1.jpg&h=bca614a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/174125_99fdbdaf90b010c330ddde8dfc252063.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F174125_99fdbdaf90b010c330ddde8dfc252063.jpg&h=3903dd56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家個情況唔係好樂觀，係澳門搵過流浪狗義工幫手，但而家佢地表示唐狗本身無乜人會領養，加上如果佢仍然癱瘓既話狗場都難以接收，同埋都唔可能放番佢番去佢原來生活既地方<br />\n<br />\n老虎仔係一隻好乖好得意既唐狗黎的，佢本身好精靈活潑，我真係好想幫到佢...<br />\n<br />\n下面係老虎仔未病前既相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/174702_63b38b1eb3351305712651c5f0751eb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F174702_63b38b1eb3351305712651c5f0751eb7.jpg&h=bbe07784&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/174703_2d062653e54ecf8e1d87d174b328aa23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F174703_2d062653e54ecf8e1d87d174b328aa23.jpg&h=e6aed990&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/174704_d035b0ac5b0838fe4a61198b6fd82c71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F174704_d035b0ac5b0838fe4a61198b6fd82c71.jpg&h=3737411c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/174705_2713e8c855e601a92f69c0cf27f199c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F174705_2713e8c855e601a92f69c0cf27f199c0.jpg&h=fbadb3eb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/16/174706_0f93ef972d4faabb769f27b14502f070.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F16%2F174706_0f93ef972d4faabb769f27b14502f070.jpg&h=7ea26014&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我而家應該點做？有無巴打可以比d意見我？[/quote]"},{"pid":"4ea6ee6855894ae7ace90f2e58739f3d328e39c2","tid":404494,"uid":35508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:58:34.000Z","msg":"原本係一隻好優秀既唐狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7036b0d92f2119f88de0e16fa95f1940dc2f0009","tid":404494,"uid":58609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:00:19.000Z","msg":"澳門有冇Fb收養流浪狗動物gp啊？post上去睇下有冇人要"},{"pid":"3c61b53f37872d15c3091dc06b5a07b223da5583","tid":404494,"uid":77861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:01:57.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"223e5894d2fc957a0cfc72675947c5a1ffb446ef","tid":404494,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:02:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1757bcf388edf086688c69333ac57c2a4d6418","tid":404494,"uid":38248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:11:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳門有冇Fb收養流浪狗動物gp啊？post上去睇下有冇人要</blockquote><br />\n我地有問過，但感覺唔想幫，佢反問我地救狗前有無思前想後"},{"pid":"5f9fd3e400c053fce6ba17110ef98d9a794469c2","tid":404494,"uid":70811,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:22:45.000Z","msg":"啲動物義工真係好虛偽，見係唐狗就唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好地地身體健康嘅就唔洗搵義工幫手啦"},{"pid":"647a4871c70dde40dbfb150baa49417501bb1694","tid":404494,"uid":70811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T07:24:00.000Z","msg":"醫返好佢之後，俾佢返返去同家人團聚生活得唔得？"},{"pid":"fc657d470767fd10c5793a0f066d37901d4c0cc6","tid":404494,"uid":38248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T08:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醫返好佢之後，俾佢返返去同家人團聚生活得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n佢家人原本有七隻，而家得番四隻<br />\n個到生活環境唔好，其他狗仲好健康，唯獨呢隻有事<br />\n其實諗住接佢番香港照顧，雖然對其他狗仔可能唔公平，但係老虎仔最需要人照顧，係我地能力範圍內希望幫到就幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29112919de9debac6fad0daa4c68028930bd67b5","tid":404494,"uid":26766,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T08:13:03.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> d撚樣食屎啦,一見唐狗就唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510da3d6ad04664cffa7bbfd298ed4b232cfc383","tid":404494,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T08:14:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>澳門有冇Fb收養流浪狗動物gp啊？post上去睇下有冇人要</blockquote><br />\n我地有問過，但感覺唔想幫，佢反問我地救狗前有無思前想後</blockquote><br />\n乜撚嘢思前想後"},{"pid":"ebb27185b2a54cc34340ec5ed5427fd9e87f1793","tid":404494,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T08:14:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>醫返好佢之後，俾佢返返去同家人團聚生活得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n佢家人原本有七隻，而家得番四隻<br />\n個到生活環境唔好，其他狗仲好健康，唯獨呢隻有事<br />\n其實諗住接佢番香港照顧，雖然對其他狗仔可能唔公平，但係老虎仔最需要人照顧，係我地能力範圍內希望幫到就幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會得番4隻"},{"pid":"b35ed63810259a69ef0878ed5a52d891d8140bc1","tid":404494,"uid":38248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T08:16:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>醫返好佢之後，俾佢返返去同家人團聚生活得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n佢家人原本有七隻，而家得番四隻<br />\n個到生活環境唔好，其他狗仲好健康，唯獨呢隻有事<br />\n其實諗住接佢番香港照顧，雖然對其他狗仔可能唔公平，但係老虎仔最需要人照顧，係我地能力範圍內希望幫到就幫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解會得番4隻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有一隻上次見佢個咀卡住左舊骨，想捉佢但佢走左，之後就搵唔番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01420083159cad92cc83d1b2d59a5df8b2380d72","tid":404494,"uid":38248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T08:18:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> d撚樣食屎啦,一見唐狗就唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔撚明咩叫唐狗bb都唔會有人要，更何況成左年仲要癱左既唐狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3247cf09da7f8f8aea8ea19561101ed47a4e7d12","tid":404494,"uid":26766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T08:57:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> d撚樣食屎啦,一見唐狗就唔要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔撚明咩叫唐狗bb都唔會有人要，更何況成左年仲要癱左既唐狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nD人係咁架啦,把口就愛動物咪又係睇種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor